visual_elements.description: Plan view diagram of a carport parking space showing a car parked within a rectangular space. The diagram highlights two corner columns on the left side, with dimensions indicating a minimum 20 feet open space vertically and an unspecified horizontal 'open' dimension. The driveway/parking surface is indicated at the bottom right of the space.

Left side elevation view of a covered parking space under a carport. Shows a car parked under a roof supported by two corner columns. The roof bottom system is labeled. Vertical clearance is marked as minimum 7 feet open, and horizontal clearance is marked as minimum 20 feet open.

Front elevation view of a covered parking space under a carport. Shows a car parked under a sloped roof supported by two corner columns. The roof bottom system is labeled. Vertical clearance is marked as minimum 7 feet open, and horizontal clearance is marked as minimum 10 feet open.
